<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA87">
<l>kalantu maṇiyimaikkuṅ kaṇṇāniṉ mēṉi</l>
<l>malarntu marakatamē kāṭṭu – nalantikaḻuṅ</l>
<l>kontiṉvāy vaṇṭaṟaiyun taṇṭuḻāyk kōmāṉai</l>
<l>yantivāṉ kāṭṭu matu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Kaṇṇaṉ, on whom the jewel diffusely twinkles, your body</l>
<l>in bloom shows itself as an emerald. The sky at dusk is</l>
<l>what shows the king with cool tulsi, where bees hum</l>
<l>on the garland strings glittering with beauty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
